{"name":"本多忠勝","nameCn":"本多忠胜","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/c3/6f/74590_crt_fZA85.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>本多忠胜</li><li><span>别名: </span>平八郎</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>锅之助</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>本多 忠勝</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ほんだ ただかつ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Honda Tadakatsu</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>生日: </span>1548年3月17日</li>","detail":"本多忠胜（1548年3月17日－1610年12月3日）是日本战国时代和江户时代前期的武将和大名。德川氏谱代家臣。上总国大多喜藩初代藩主、伊势国桑名藩初代藩主。忠胜系本多家宗家初代，本姓藤原氏，也是德川四天王、德川十六神将、德川三杰以及日本七柱枪之一。许多强敌给予忠胜高额的评价，武田信玄给予忠胜的评价：“效忠家康太可惜。”、织田信长给予忠胜的评价：“日本之张飞、华实兼备的猛将。”丰臣秀吉给予忠胜的评价：“古今独步之壮士。”","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/94507","name":"徳川家康","nameCn":"德川家康","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/aa/a9/94507_G9rhy.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/223711","name":"関ヶ原","nameCn":"关原","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/20/61/223711_9VUwN.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/52128","name":"太閤記","nameCn":"太阁记","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/cc/fc/52128_YfI31.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/30490","name":"秀吉","nameCn":"秀吉","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/36/88/30490_It7h0.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/121624","name":"影武者徳川家康","nameCn":"影武者德川家康","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/23/6e/121624_g2gve.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/94516","name":"武田信玄","nameCn":"武田信玄","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d1/a4/94516_A2Jj2.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":6},{"href":"/subject/127903","name":"真田丸","nameCn":"真田丸","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/2b/fb/127903_2ljHS.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":""